For the assessment, the following reports and guidelines were reviewed.

-  MoFEC (June 2009), Financial Transparency and Accountability Perception Survey;
-  MoFEC  (July  2009),  Follow-up  Study  to  Monitor  Improvements  in  Financial Transparency and Accountability Based on Woreda City Benchmarking Survey, Draft
-  MoFEC  (August  2009),  Financial  Transparency  &amp;  Accountability:  Laypersons' budget and expenditure templates. Prototype design document;
-  MoFEC (2009), Media Disclosure Strategy and Guidebook;
-  MoFEC (ND), Financial Transparency &amp; Accountability Implementation Assessment Report, Revised Final Report;
-  Ministry of Civil Service in Collaboration with PSCAP Donors (Nov. 2011), "Woreda and City Administrations Benchmarking Survey IV‖: Supply Side Report;
-  Ministry of Civil Service in Collaboration with PSCAP Donors (Nov. 2011), "Woreda and  City  Administrations  Benchmarking  Survey  IV‖:  Citizens  Report  Card  (CRC) Report;
-  Ministry of Civil Service in Collaboration with PSCAP Donors (Nov. 2011), "Woreda and City Administrations Benchmarking Survey IV‖: KII and FGD Report;
-  MoFEC  (August 2017), Impact Assessment on Financial Transparency and Accountability (FTA) Implementation, Final Report;

-  በጋም/ሕ/ብ/ክ/መንግስት የገን/ኢኮ/ልማ/ቢሮ ( ታህሳስ 2008 ) ፣ የተሻሻለዉ የበጀት ወጪ እና አገልግሎት አቅርቦት መረጃ አመላካች ማኑዋል ፣ PBS-III: የፋይናንስ ግልጽነትና ተጠያቂነት ፕሮጀክት፤
-  የገንዘብና ኢኮኖሚ ልማት ሚኒስቴር (ነሐሴ 2001)፣ በክልል ደረጃ የሚካሄደውን የበጀት ዝግጅት ሂደት አስመልክቶ የተዘጋጀ መመሪያ፣ ለክልሎች የተዘጋጀ ናሙና፤
-  የወረዳ  ገንዘብና  ኢኮኖሚ  ልማት  ጽ/ቤቶች  (ND)፣  በቅድመ  በጀት  ሂደት  ዜጎችን ለማወያየት የተዘጋጀ፣ የአሠራር መመሪያ፤
-  የገንዘብና ኢኮኖሚ ልማት ሚኒስቴር (መስከረም 2009)፣ የክልልና ወረዳ የመንግስት በጀት መረጃን በመገናኛ ብዙሃን፣ ለህዝብ ማሳወቅ፤
